        <h1>VC3</h1>
        <p class="lead">A project to automatically <em>discover</em>,
<em>provision</em>, and <em>manage</em> the resources to build virtual
clusters&#8212;dynamic, infrastructures that enable extreme scale scientific
computation.</p>
