        <h2><small>Resource</small><br>Provisioning</h2>
        <p>Build an autonomous software agent that can provision resources with
general guidance from scientists. Provisioning will be flexible, resilient,
high throughput, and rapidly reconfigurable at runtime.</p>


        <p><a href="provisioning.html">VCC and resource provisioning &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
